Review comment:
       Object media (aka data, aka contents) are immutable once created, so the mtime could be initialized from `o->time_created()`.  Object metadata is not immutable, and when changed it resets `o->updated()`.  I am not sure which one you wanted so I went with `o->updated()`, I can change it if you think `o->time_created()` is a better choice.




